{"tid":235783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人既歡樂係有限既","createTime":"2017-05-09T09:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T16:29:53.000Z","uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab0e18555a84ae3b86f6274f4e05312ccec0df3","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"但2個人既樂趣係無限既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩同fd講起一個人自由自在個感覺<br />\n定係拍拖個種全心全意開心d<br />\n作為拍過一次拖之後dry左n年既人<br />\n我敢講絕對係拍拖既感覺遠遠好過自己一個人<br />\n一個人既好處唔講啦 黎黎去去都係個d <br />\n不過真係自在既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但耐左個心真係會麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始對生活失去興趣 根本唔知生活咁辛苦為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖最大一個好處就係令自己有一個生活目標<br />\n幾辛苦都好 都會頂落去 只要另一半過到好生活咩都可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自己一個人係唔會有呢個感覺 一但burn out左真係會自棄自棄 因為覺得世上已經冇野好care 同時唔會有人care我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdd73667d272286bff2e9b94d50a117758d34c6","tid":235783,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"你人生幾空虛"},{"pid":"0016d96cee20aaaae68dc83e26c0a3cb97987f84","tid":235783,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"有女=日日都歡樂"},{"pid":"4b6daa1db8d41216337abe2c5db1bd6d1b3854d5","tid":235783,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"有之以為利 (Probability)<br />\n無之以為用 (Availability)"},{"pid":"ec304b5eae112236aa47083f91b7bc1e4496cff1","tid":235783,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"我明"},{"pid":"f21f242d4074addf9eac2de4c79ee07430f303e6","tid":235783,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28619d1439764373c7c371b4011b6acde09383a6","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你人生幾空虛</blockquote><br />\n如果唔係為兩老 我應該死左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbb1e8e234d05bf344783cf7e05e1890554df64","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有之以為利 (Probability)<br />\n無之以為用 (Availability)</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1f0a0a4f61000ae4f12fe29753cd8cd61e30f1","tid":235783,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你人生幾空虛</blockquote><br />\n如果唔係為兩老 我應該死左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"a6ca1e43cdc9c37c903db2c2cf1f457b928a7e5c","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有女=日日都歡樂</blockquote><br />\n咁又未必<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有時煩起上黎真係想一巴煎落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但overall黎講 伴侶比到你既好野遠遠大於麻煩野 特別心靈方面"},{"pid":"80a29092a59ad2fdcacea797a09189e166c01f61","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02e0918847cfee6f489683fe646ae50a268a501","tid":235783,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日solo都好充實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔明"},{"pid":"7617dbed8a8fe5dedb5ca690a9465d50652a260a","tid":235783,"uid":