pid":"adbf5fd5dd1caf048eef05c0cee28069d77be28e","tid":235783,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>活著就是痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過真係完全唔再理感情<br />\n係另外一d方面搵人生目標<br />\n例如要自己第時出人頭地<br />\n不過伴侶真係最直接最有效既人生動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2818e12cd21545157905920ea5df52c1ccdb43df","tid":235783,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n把口就講到單身有幾feel又好enjoy<br />\n其實心底好想有個人錫下 <br />\n但ex帶比我既傷害實在太深<br />\n依家已經唔敢信人 唔敢愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2de9e79b4926359f8b152898bafa862dde58447","tid":235783,"uid":59670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n把口就講到單身有幾free又好enjoy<br />\n其實心底好想有個人錫下 <br />\n但ex帶比我既傷害實在太深<br />\n依家已經唔敢信人 唔敢愛人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}